{"tid":1777073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（超緊急）跟進藍衫美國白人手足被指襲警事件","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T04:00:23.000Z","uid":306474,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"097a6f884129a9f9a4b078eb83be7a524777ee7b","tid":1777073,"uid":306474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"大家好，想問有無人幫手搵到片，證明到手足當時無郁手打持警棍冒警男子，及襲擊另一個呀叔。同埋最好影到冒警男子事後先拎委任証出黎果一刻。<br />\n<br />\n藍衫係我同事，見當時好多人拍片，有其他有利於單官司既片段對佢真係好重要，佢係真心支持香港人爭取民主，有無人可以pm其他角度既片俾我，謝謝你！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPsgROo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPsgROo.png&h=615af397&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9daf189c6514a441e8a1af0b36a27452369055c6","tid":1777073,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:24:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6efd6d87f4fdd6cd41a4fcd3fb261f8b02e0de6","tid":1777073,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:26:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"add76f1f237c6a465a00f1fe22ea82e420f04972","tid":1777073,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"仲有7個鐘就係啦... 跪求大家入嚟睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hy3vV3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHy3vV3M.jpg&h=7e318a13&s={SIZE}\" />唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n好重要今晚就係啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*已獲不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【國際人權日．正日集會】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1948年12月10日，聯合國公佈《世界人權宣言》，確立生而為人的基本權利。走過71年，世界人權仍然是未竟之路。在香港及世界各地，人民仍要為爭取基本的自由及權利奮鬥，甚至有所付出及犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n12月10日晚，我們一起站出來，為香港人加油，也為全球為人權奮鬥的人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：12月10日<br />\n時間：18:30-22:00<br />\n地點：金鐘連儂牆下<br />\n</span><br />\n內容：<br />\n悼念及回顧<br />\n嘉賓講話<br />\n短片欣賞及分享<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPK0vx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPK0vx.jpg&h=63585984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推呀屌你再過7個鐘就係啦 唔好再屌鬼啦行動post呢文宣post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係完咗人權日遊行就end game㗎<br />\n我地仲有訴求㗎！！！<br />\n聽日要見到連儂牆有十萬人呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12月10號 6點半政總見！！"},{"pid":"ccd8435606e6c8195e46803bf2da7789baa16b69","tid":1777073,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8d83671bc2cdc3a207fa4450289a9d8705aefab","tid":1777073,"uid":306474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}